00:05:52.920 --> 00:05:55.170 align:middle line:90%
connecting to gratitude.

00:05:55.170 --> 00:05:56.770 align:middle line:90%
>> So that's a great connection.

00:05:56.770 --> 00:06:02.260 align:middle line:84%
Now, it's a little tricky in
that often gratitude comes,

00:06:02.260 --> 00:06:04.600 align:middle line:90%
