00:06:11.850 --> 00:06:16.200 align:middle line:84%
is it comes through
cultivation of awareness.

00:06:16.200 --> 00:06:20.400 align:middle line:84%
But what we don't realize is
that, within our own awareness,

00:06:20.400 --> 00:06:23.280 align:middle line:84%
we have all these
potentials, and it's

00:06:23.280 --> 00:06:25.710 align:middle line:84%
through the cultivation
of awareness,

00:06:25.710 --> 00:06:27.870 align:middle line:84%
and not just being
aware of things,

00:06:27.870 --> 00:06:30.630 align:middle line:84%
but cultivation of
consciousness itself,

00:06:30.630 --> 00:06:36.030 align:middle line:84%
that really is the foundation of
our fulfillment, the foundation

00:06:36.030 --> 00:06:40.530 align:middle line:84%
of our evolution, our
growth, and, ultimately,

00:06:40.530 --> 00:06:43.590 align:middle line:90%
the foundation of our health.

00:06:43.590 --> 00:06:46.650 align:middle line:84%
>> I love that because I
remember when I first started

00:06:46.650 --> 00:06:49.080 align:middle line:84%
