00:06:52.530 --> 00:06:55.080 align:middle line:84%
just remember reading
some of them and thinking,

00:06:55.080 --> 00:07:00.150 align:middle line:84%
this sounds really kind of
impossible when it was being

00:07:00.150 --> 00:07:03.820 align:middle line:84%
