qualities of our humanity

00:07:43.440 --> 00:07:47.290 align:middle line:90%
like emotions and relationships?

00:07:47.290 --> 00:07:50.460 align:middle line:84%
>> So we're really talking
about the relationship to life

00:07:50.460 --> 00:07:52.570 align:middle line:90%
and all aspects of it.

00:07:52.570 --> 00:07:56.940 align:middle line:84%
And too often what happens
when we're challenged

00:07:56.940 --> 00:07:59.550 align:middle line:90%
is that we go into resistance.

00:07:59.550 --> 00:08:01.090 align:middle line:90%
We resist the anger.

00:08:01.090 --> 00:08:02.340 align:middle line:90%
Oh, we're not supposed to be--

00:08:02.340 --> 00:08:03.450 align:middle line:90%
we're supposed to be peaceful.

00:08:03.450 --> 00:08:04.825 align:middle line:84%
We're not supposed
to be violent.

00:08:04.825 --> 00:08:08.880 align:middle line:84%
We resist the challenge,
the physical challenge.

00:08:08.880 --> 00:08:10.080 align:middle line:90%
We resist the disease.

00:08:10.080 --> 00:08:11.160 align:middle line:90%
We resist.

00:08:11.160 --> 00:08:15.750 align:middle line:84%
And when we live in
resistance, that's

00:08:15.750 --> 00:08:20.320 align:middle line:84%
when we actually create
more of the suffering.

00:08:20.320 --> 00:08:27.090 align:middle line:84%
And so the way out is
actually a combination

00:08:27.090 --> 00:08:31.170 align:middle line:90%
of cultivating consciousness.

00:08:31.170 --> 00:08:39.330 align:middle line:84%
It's also cultivating the
qualities of the heart.

00:08:39.330 --> 00:08:46.170 align:middle line:84%
It's also cultivating and
reprogramming the mind such

00:08:46.170 --> 00:08:51.120 align:middle line:84%
that we relate to life in
a totally different way.

00:08:51.120 --> 00:08:54.600 align:middle line:84%
And let me just explain
this with a question

00:08:54.600 --> 00:08:57.790 align:middle line:84%
that I often pose
to my students.

00:08:57.790 --> 00:09:03.630 align:middle line:84%
If you knew every challenge,
every problem in your life,

00:09:03.630 --> 00:09:06.720 align:middle line:84%
every experience in
your life was organized

00:09:06.720 --> 00:09:11.280 align:middle line:84%
by your soul for your
learning and growth,

00:09:11.280 --> 00:09:15.120 align:middle line:84%
that you actually planned
it before this life,

00:09:15.120 --> 00:09:16.750 align:middle line:90%
how would your life change?

00:09:16.750 --> 00:09:19.810 align:middle line:84%
How would your relationship
to life change?

00:09:19.810 --> 00:09:22.510 align:middle line:84%
And what I hear from
them is, oh my gosh,

00:09:22.510 --> 00:09:27.000 align:middle line:84%
if I really knew that, if
I really accepted that,

00:09:27.000 --> 00:09:29.910 align:middle line:90%
then I would drop the worry.

00:09:29.910 --> 00:09:32.290 align:middle line:90%
I would drop the resistance.

00:09:32.290 --> 00:09:34.800 align:middle line:90%
I would begin to embrace life.

00:09:34.800 --> 00:09:38.490 align:middle line:84%
I'd begin to embrace
every moment of life.

00:09:38.490 --> 00:09:41.220 align:middle line:84%
And so the key to
be able to have

00:09:41.220 --> 00:09:44.160 align:middle line:84%
that kind of radical
acceptance and to really

00:09:44.160 --> 00:09:49.100 align:middle line:84%
be embracing of life is
built on a foundation of,

00:09:49.100 --> 00:09:53.190 align:middle line:84%
first, cultivating the nervous
system through meditation,

00:09:53.190 --> 00:09:54.960 align:middle line:84%
through a type of
meditation that

00:09:54.960 --> 00:09:59.190 align:middle line:84%
gives the mind rest, that
allows us to go beyond thought

00:09:59.190 --> 00:10:01.840 align:middle line:90%
and feeling and sensation.

00:10:01.840 --> 00:10:07.230 align:middle line:84%
It's based, then, on integrating
what we gain in the meditation

00:10:07.230 --> 00:10:10.500 align:middle line:90%
into every moment of the life.

00:10:10.500 --> 00:10:14.160 align:middle line:84%
And that's accelerated
by practices

00:10:14.160 --> 00:10:17.590 align:middle line:84%
that allow us to come
into the heart, that

00:10:17.590 --> 00:10:21.280 align:middle line:84%
allow us to connect
with and integrate

00:10:21.280 --> 00:10:24.900 align:middle line:84%
that true self through the
heart and the heart's love.

